so even now as i'm looking at this little gadget and hopefully you can see me looking at you rather than away from you i'm also hearing what i'm saying and thinking what i'm saying all this comes together as as one person looking seeing thinking but in buddhist psychology the millions you know thousands of little consciousnesses that run so rapidly together to give us the impression of continuity

