touches the body and perceives um form light well we'll come to that in a minute so it's the same with the ear the um the sensitive part whatever it's called the drum or something uh all that is actually sensitive to are the incoming waves of pressure um from the air around that's all we're going to that a bit more uh deeply in a bit

